The paper presents a LiDAR data set for complex urban environments, which is relevant to robotics and autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of 2D and 3D LiDAR sensors, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) applications. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of simultaneous localization and mapping (SLAM) algorithms, which are relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
